ier": "ritesh-mudgal-a2883731", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAa1WAABR_GKwObyvuTWw9nsQkeu2o_YsoA", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHLaikBMaY-AxWhzyCVNFcn2EdzeSRFsJ0", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/first_name": "Neha", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/follower_count": "2865", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/headline": "Human Resources Coordinator", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/last_name": "Singh", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/profile_picture": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFaXJw7TzsWtQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1688191938237?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=QDcV1Qr-glSDacfu7utRP38l2N8Zmx56xr1xEywTJSQ", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "neha-singh-8890bba", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAHLaikBMaY-AxWhzyCVNFcn2EdzeSRFsJ0", "publicIdentifier": "karinvanzyl", "recommendations/0/context": "Karin worked with Priti on the same team", "recommendations/0/date": "December 25, 2022", "recommendations/0/description": "As General Manager of Amanbagh, India, I worked with Priti from February 2019 until July 2020. In her capacity as Sales Manager based in the UK, we worked together on events in London and also a roadshow in the UK. I can recommend her for a similar position", "recommendations/0/name": "Priti Bhudia", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Product Manager", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/priti-bhudia-63206635/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdOIgYBmGq1JpU_Cjk_Z_epA2U_Xn35sIU", "recommendations/1/context": "Karin managed Rajendra directly", "recommendations/1/date": "April 16, 2022", "recommendations/1/description": "I was privileged to work with Raj for 5 years at Amanbagh. As Director of Human Resources first for Amanbagh and later for both Aman properties in India, he excelled in his role. As a mature manager, he was respected not only by his peers but by senior management within the group. He is an excellent listener and excels in his interpersonal relationships and ability to bring employees from different departments together to work in harmony. He stays calm in conflict situations, is a ‘solution thinker’, creative planner and trusted confidante. I would not hesitate to recommend Rajendra for a similar situation and if the opportunity arises, would love to work with him again!", "recommendations/1/name": "Rajendra Madhur", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Leading HR Strategy and Talent Development for Sustainable Hospitality", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajendra-madhur-32687224/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUcZk4Boy8gepNueeaydXNVQGfKOFzXZt8", "recommendations/2/context": "Karin managed Ritesh directly", "recommendations/2/date": "April 27, 2021", "recommendations/2/description": "As General Manager of Amanbagh in India, I had the opportunity to work with Ritesh on two different occasions. First as F&B manager and a couple of years later, we re-employed Ritesh as Executive Assistant Manager. With his excellent interpersonal relationships (with peers, subordinates and guests) and his ability to stay calm in challenging situations, it was a pleasure to have Ritesh on the team. He has a ‘leave it to me, I will get it done’ attitude, pays attention to detail and has exceptional communication skills. I found him mature, responsible and with a great sense of humour. An asset to the hospitality industry who I will employ again should the opportunity arise.", "recommendations/2/name": "Ritesh Mudgal", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Luxury Hotelier", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ritesh-mudgal-a2883731/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAa1WAABR_GKwObyvuTWw9nsQkeu2o_YsoA", "recommendations/3/context": "Karin was senior to Sandrine but didn't manage Sandrine directly", "recommendations/3/date": "November 16, 2020", "recommendations/3/description": "As General Manager of Amanbagh, India, I had the privilege of working with Sandrine for 5 years. With her passion and knowledge of the hospitality industry, her extended network (specially in Hong Kong, Singapore, Thailand, Indonesia and India) and her positive energy, she managed to exponentially grow the marketshare of the AMAN properties in these markets. She has creative ideas and is very detail oriented which results in fast response times and the creation of “out of the box” campaigns and events. I would be delighted to work with Sandrine again should the opportunity arise and would not hesitate to recommend her for a similar position. ", "recommendations/3/name": "Sandrine Boutin", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Director of Sales & Marketing and Regional Sales Roles | Driving growth in Ultra-Luxury | Strategic Partnerships | Leadership | Connector", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandrineboutin/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADrCNIB0NHE-ybJcjNZPl4Q9fJD-LTgb9g", "recommendations/4/context": "Karin managed I Gede directly", "recommendations/4/date": "April 18, 2014", "recommendations/4/description": "Wisnawa is a competent and very dedicated Financial Controller who showed amazing loyalty in adverse conditions. He was fully in charge of the finance department during his tenure with Ubud Hanging Gardens and ensured that reports were completed in a timely manner. Wisnawa is a strong leader who stays calm in stressful situations. His great interpersonal relationships results in him being respected and popular with his peers and subordinates. Due to his logical thinking he can also assist with serious human resource issues.\nI can recommend him for a similar position at any time and would love to work with him again should the opportunity arise.", "recommendations/4/name": "I Gede Wisnawa", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Director of Finance", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/i-gede-wisnawa-10672b2a/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAYooNYB2zxcRPQ4nLQ_8IqEHm6Mbk_ZEWc", "recommendations/5/context": "Karin managed Emmanuel directly", "recommendations/5/date": "January 9, 2014", "recommendations/5/description": "I had the privilege of working with Emmanuel at Ubud Hanging Gardens in Bali. Emmanuel is a creative leader and excellent trainer who developed a strong and loyal team. He is focussed on guest satisfaction and strives to make the impossible possible. With a good understanding of cost control and budgets  he came up with innovative ideas to increase revenue and profits. I wish him only the best for his future career and would not hesitate to employ Emmanuel again if the opportunity arises.", "recommendations/5/name": "Emmanuel Baroiller", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "What does 2024 have in store for us?", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/emmanuel-baroiller-4298762a/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAYt4eEB3KlvjZhP4VHZvuIGDqmBH_Pj24Q", "recommendations/6/context": "Karin was Erwin's client", "recommendations/6/date": "September 24, 2012", "recommendations/6/description": "Erwin is a good manager with good insights in his field", "recommendations/6/name": "Erwin Adnan", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Front Office | Revenue Management | Sales | Distribution | Overseas Experiences", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/erwin-adnan-66a2b556/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAvKWHIBe2MDi2YPFL0SWJd9Mkhv0_cXWes", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Rajendra worked with Karin on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "December 1, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Karin is a very influential personality and she has ability to make things possible with her determination, sincerity and hard work. A true inspirational hospitality leader who has served for more than 25 years as General Manager. She is very caring and keeps the team motivating to achieve higher targets. We worked together in Aman and I personally found her very professional, caring for both staff and guest, I am pretty impressed with her planning and time management. Kudos to her! ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Rajendra Madhur", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Leading HR Strategy and Talent Development for Sustainable Hospitality", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajendra-madhur-32687224/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUcZk4Boy8gepNueeaydXNVQGfKOFzXZt8", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Karin was senior to Sandrine but didn't manage Sandrine directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "November 12, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Karin over 5 years at AMAN. Karin was a great General Manager, extremely dynamic and very hands-on as well as close to all the team members on property and extremely respected by all of them. She was involved in Sales of course and was always very responsive and active with the sales team, always looking at how to increase the hotel's performance. I would love to work again with Karin. ", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Sandrine Boutin", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Director of Sales & Marketing and Regional Sales Roles | Driving growth in Ultra-Luxury | Strategic Partnerships | Leadership | Connector", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandrineboutin/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADrCNIB0NHE-ybJcjNZPl4Q9fJD-LTgb9g", "skills/0/title": "Hospitality Industry", "skills/1/title": "Front Office", "skills/2/title": "Opening Hotels", "skills/3/title": "Resorts", "skills/4/title": "Banquets", "skills/5/title": "Pre-opening", "skills/6/title": "Hotels", "skills/7/title": "Revenue Analysis", "skills/8/title": "Food & Beverage", "skills/9/title": "Hotel Management", "skills/10/title": "Hospitality", "skills/11/title": "Hospitality Management", "skills/12/tit